name: CHAPTER # 001: UNEXPECTED SAVIOR
description:
“what is that?”

this is a story about the savior who came to a little meta's country, and trying to save a man from the nightmare that befell him. he has no food, no water, no family and no friend. everything has been stolen by the king of nightmare. 

"water! food! thank you so much!"

“do you have a name?”
“i’m kianthe, the savior of light”

unexpected savior will come into your life.
